- Near IR (NIR, IR-A): 0.75-1.4um, Night vision goggles, fiber optics
- Short-Wavelength IR (SWIR, IR-B): 1.4-3um, High water absorption,
  long-distance telecommunication
- Mid-Wavelength IR (MWIR, IR-C): 3-8um, heat-seeking missiles
- Long-Wavelenght IR (LWIR, IR-C): 8-15um, termal imaging
- Far-Infrared (FIR): 15-1000um, black body radiation of interstellar gases
